Services:
  1.it enable communication between varius components within and outside of the application.
  1. It helps connects application together with other applications & users.
  3. for example in our application groups of pods running like frontend group pods, dbackend group of pods.
  4. you can not acccess webapplication running in pod from your laptop beacause pods in other network you can accces it only from node.

Nord Port service:
  it helps us access pod by mapping port.
  webserver running in pods at 80 port it is target port
  2nd ports is service ports. it has ip address is called cluster ip of service.
  port on the node itself is called node port 30000-32767

YML file to create service

apiVersion: v1
kind: Service
metadata:
  name: app-service

spec:
  type: Nodeport
  ports:
  - targetPort: 80  
    port: 80
    nodePort: 30008
  selector:
    pull lable from pod.yml file



